These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
House: modern, wooden, colonial, cottage
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, coffee, iced-tea
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the modern house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the wooden house is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| House          | cottage | colonial | wooden | modern   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | mirinda     | coffee   | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, pear, pineapple, lime
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, bridge, canasta
1. the person eating lime is the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating lime##1
4. the person eating lime is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | pineapple | lime | pear | onion    |
| Game   | bridge    | monopoly      | billiard | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, jet-ski, airplane
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, bellflower, daffodil
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person driving the tram is the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport         | tram | airplane | jet-ski   | motorbike |
| Flower   | azalea   | bellflower | daffodil | rose         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, skydiving, cooking, gardening
4 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, hamster, dog
1. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | gardening | skydiving | baking  | cooking      |
| Pet         | snake | dog   | hamster | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, water, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, hip-hop, rock
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta | water | juice | mirinda |
| Music-Genre    | soul       | rock | hip-hop | d&b     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, game, bongani, dannemann
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, blueberry, potato, grapefruit
1. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | dannemann | bongani | dunhill | game |
| Food           | pumpkin      | potato | grapefruit | blueberry    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
City: hannover, paris, nizza, london
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, cricket, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| City   | nizza | paris | hannover | london  |
| Sport           | cricket | baseball | snowboarding       | cycling |

