3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the victorian house##1
5. the cottage house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| City         | edinburgh | paris      | nizza | venice |
| House   | cottage          | victorian | wooden     | townhouse    |

