.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, almond-milk, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, chef, lawyer, entrepreneur
1. the entrepreneur is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the police-officer##1
3. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
4. the chef is on the left of the lawyer##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk    | almond-milk       | hot-chocolate | water   |
| Job     | chef | lawyer | entrepreneur   | police-officer |

