.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, lily, dahlia
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, chess, board-games, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Flower    | bellflower | lily  | iris | dahlia |
| Hobby   | fishing | board-games | chess          | reading    |

