.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, fish, rat
4 different games are played: poker, scrabble, snooker, backgammon
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Pet      | fish | chinchilla  | dog | rat |
| Game   | poker  | snooker | backgammon           | scrabble   |

