.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, writing, reading, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, train, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Hobby   | writing | skydiving | singing | reading  |
| Transport           | quad-bike | skateboard      | train | bike |

