.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, september, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, skateboarding, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | september | may  | march | july   |
| Sport        | skateboarding | lacrosse | weightlifting    | handball |

