3. the person traveling to hamburg is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| City          | berlin | hannover  | hamburg  | miami |
| Pet   | guinea-pig   | turtle | goldfish | chinchilla   |

