.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, bridge, backgammon
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, cat, rat
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Game   | bridge | backgammon     | monopoly | billiard |
| Pet         | rat | bird | guinea-pig   | cat   |

