.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, cycling, rugby, badminton
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, pony, hamster
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | cycling | rugby | badminton | rowing |
| Pet   | hamster     | pony    | ferret      | goldfish   |

