.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, fish, turtle, bird
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, journalist, lawyer, teacher
1. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the journalist is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the bird is the teacher##1
5. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Pet   | pony | turtle | fish | bird   |
| Job     | lawyer  | scientist    | journalist       | teacher |

 